detail.name: Gotenks
detail.effect:
[Permanent] If you have 10 or more cards in your Drop, this card gets +5000 power.
[On Play] Place the top 2 cards of your deck into their owner's Drop. Then, choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with a cost of 3 or less and place it at the bottom of its owner's deck.

detail.name: ゴテンクス
detail.effect: 【永続】自分のドロップのカードが10枚以上の場合、このカードのパワー+5000。【登場時】自分のデッキの上から2枚をドロップに置く。その後、相手のコスト3以下のバトルカード1枚までを選び、デッキの下に置く。
